divs: Sighting DetailsMy friend was taking pictures of their new land they had just bought in Canton, Tx. First picture is of her boyfriend removing the "For Sale" sign. You can see the small black dot in the upper right corner of the picture. Second picture is of him after tossing the "For Sale" sign on the ground. Here you can see the object very well. She did not notice the object in either picture until the film was developed. She didn't know what to do with the pictures until I told her they should be seen by someone just in case it is something.
